CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, October 20, 1951, pg. 15, reads: "Press Party - When L'Tanya, famous modiste and designer, was in Pittsburgh last week, she was honored at a Press Party at the Fort Pitt Hotel, sponsored by the Urban League under whose auspices her 'Cavalcade of Fashions,' is being presented on Oct. 26. Top photo, left to right: Alexander J. Allen, executive secretary of the Urban League; Florence Sando, WDTV television star; Mary Dee, WHOD; L'Tanya, Earsley Kincaid, WLOA; Jane Gibson, KQV, and Vickie Corey, KDKA... - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait, from left: Alexander J. Allen, Florence Sando, Mary Dee, L'Tanya, Earsley Kincaid, Jane Gibson, and Vickie Corey, seated at banquet table for Press Party in Fort Pitt Hotel
